Title: Tightrope - Accurate ChIP-seq normalization
Description:
    Computational method for the normalization and analysis of ChIP-seq
    enrichments relative to experimental backgrounds, allowing accurate
    estimation of normalization factors in conditions involving global
    variations of chromatin marks.
